<DOCNO> LA032894-0043 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 026961 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
March 28, 1994, Monday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 3; Column 2; Metro Desk 
</P>
